A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering holographic bubbles of varying sizes float upward through neon-lit skyscrapers, each bubble containing abstract geometric shapes representing different concepts and innovations. The largest, brightest bubbles rise highest toward the purple and electric blue sky, while smaller, dimmer ones sink lower between the buildings. Tiny silhouettes of people on floating platforms reach toward the bubbles, some pushing them upward, others pulling them down. The scene has a rain-slicked aesthetic with reflections on dark chrome surfaces, glowing circuit-board patterns embedded in building facades, and streams of light particles flowing between the bubbles like votes being cast. The color palette emphasizes deep teals, magentas, and golden amber highlights against a dark atmospheric backdrop.
